                            <comment id="12614140" author="jimk" created="Wed, 16 Jul 2008 22:46:52 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I would vote against storing each element in a separate column. In order to access the information, you would then have to do multiple file i/o&apos;s &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;In fact, once HTableDescriptor is removed from HRegionInfo, there really won&apos;t be much left, which begs the question: is this needed at all?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12614142" author="jdcryans" created="Wed, 16 Jul 2008 22:50:53 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I don&apos;t think it will be needed anymore. +1 on closing this jira.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
